{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make it easier to end parental responsibility of absent parents",
        "additional_details": "I have heard of examples where absent parents return to their children after a number of years. We raise our children with unconditional love and we naturally want to protect them from harm. Then a stranger is allowed by law to involve themselves in the child's life.\r\n \r\nPlease help change the law and help the caring parent and their children.",
        "background": "I believe the law should be changed to make it easier for caring parents to obtain sole custody over a child if the other parent has been absent for six years or more.  ",
